se.chalmers.ait.dat215.project
Class Product

java.lang.Object
  se.chalmers.ait.dat215.project.Product

public class Product
extends java.lang.Object

The Product class represents a product that is available for purchase in the store. A product is made up of a product identification number, a product category, a name a price and the unit of the price. The IMatDataHandler creates all product objects when it is initialized.
